ESP32 UART Communication Example
Sending “Hello Pakistan” over UART using ESP-IDF
Overview

This project demonstrates basic UART communication on ESP32.
It initializes the UART with a baud rate of 115200 and sends "Hello Pakistan" every second.

Features

UART initialization with ESP-IDF

Configurable baud rate (default: 115200)

Periodic message transmission

Pin Configuration

UART Port: UART0 (default USB)

TX: Default USB TX

RX: Default USB RX

Build and Flash
idf.py build
idf.py -p COMx flash monitor

Expected Output (Serial Monitor)
Hello Pakistan
Hello Pakistan
Hello Pakistan
